<h2 align="center">ID 중복 체크...</h2><p>
<form name="idcheck">
아이디 :: <input type="text" name="userId" required="required">
<input type="button" value="중복확인" onclick="startRequest()"><p>
패스워드 :: <input type="password" name="userPass">
</form>
